node.text:
The teep is one of the most thrown techniques in Muay Thai. Just like the jab in boxing, the teep is used to set up techniques and used as both an attack and defence. 🖊 

In this video I show you common mistakes I see when people are throwing this technique and how to correct them to throw a teep like a pro. 🙌🏼

node.title: How To Teep Like A Pro With @ellisbarboza

node.text:

As a beginner it is very important that you perfect this from day one so the rest of your game can improve easily.
